    "title": "Vacancy for Teacher at IIIT Hyderabad",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at IIIT Hyderabad. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Teacher to strengthen our Dhanbad-based team.\n\nAbout IIIT Hyderabad:\nIIIT Hyderabad is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Support students with special educational needs\n• Design formative and summative assessments aligned to learning objectives\n• Contribute to school newsletter, blogs, and other publications\n• Monitor student progress and provide timely feedback\n• Maintain student records and prepare progress reports\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Lesson Planning\n• Proficiency in IB Curriculum\n• Proficiency in Data Analysis\n• Proficiency in CBSE/ICSE Standards\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in Mentoring\n• Proficiency in Curriculum Development\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Referral bonus program\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Dhanbad, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with IIIT Hyderabad!",
